# Contributing

## Development Setup

```bash
git clone https://github.com/bizprat/{{projectName}}.git
cd {{projectName}}
{{packageManager}} install
{{packageManager}} run dev
```

## Quality Gates

All changes must pass:

```bash
npm run qa:all
```

Never bypass git hooks with `--no-verify` or `--force`.

## Commit Convention

Use [Conventional Commits](https://www.conventionalcommits.org/) with these types: `feat`, `fix`, `docs`, `refactor`, `test`, `chore`.

One logical change per commit. PRs under 400 lines changed.

## Code Style

See [docs/CODING_RULES.md](docs/CODING_RULES.md) for full standards.

